videos.description: Eric Ayala knocks down a stepback 3-pointer to pad Maryland's first-half lead.
videos.headline: Ayala steps back for 3

videos.description: Thomas Kithier blocks Eric Ayala's layup to set up Xavier Tillman's floater and cap off a 7-0 Michigan State run to end the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tillman’s floater caps off 7-0 Michigan State run) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Tillman's floater caps off 7-0 Michigan State run

videos.description: Cassius Winston finds Aaron Henry in transition and he throws it down.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Henry opens 2nd half with one-handed slam) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Henry opens 2nd half with one-handed slam

videos.description: Aaron Henry picks up the offensive rebound and passes to Cassisus Winston who finds Rocket Watts in the corner for the 3-pointer to cut Maryland's lead to 43-42.
videos.headline: Watts knocks down big-time 3

videos.description: Anthony Cowan Jr. pulls up for a 3-pointer to seal Maryland's win over Michigan State.
videos.headline: Cowan nails dagger 3
